         F(\alpha)=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}e^{-\alpha t}\frac{\sin t}{t}\,dt,\;\; \alpha \ge 0. 
     F(\alpha)=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\int_{(n-1)\pi}^{n\pi}e^{-\alpha t}\frac{\sin t}{t}\,dt. 
            \lim_{\alpha\downarrow 0}F(\alpha) = F(0). 
              F'(\alpha) = -\frac{1}{1+\alpha^{2}}. 
